The report (rpt) has not been assigned yet.
The Open() method has already been called on this object.
A table being used in the report does not exist in the dataset which has been assigned to this report. (only when a dataset has been assigned to the DataSource property)
The ServerName, DatabaseName or UserId property has not been set. (only when the DataSource property has not been set)
